            S-methyl-5'-thioadenosine [CPD:C00170];
            N-isovaleryl-L-homoserine lactone [CPD:C20673]
COMMENT     The enzyme, found in the bacterium Bradyrhizobium japonicum, does not accept isovaleryl-[acyl-carrier protein] as acyl donor (cf. EC 2.3.1.184, acyl-homoserine-lactone synthase).
